data = {"time":1643602726869,"blocks":[{"id":"KcHMqlm3Gm","type":"Header","data":{"text":"Creating Groups","level":2}},{"id":"nUYR0lozNy","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"To create a group, click the \"Add a Group\" icon in the top left, located below the \"Music\" icon, and select the drop down option \"Create Group\"."}},{"id":"mTNLtnElxl","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"You can select \"New Folder\" to organize existing groups that you are in.","withBorder":false,"withBackground":true,"stretched":false}},{"id":"OUJRlnZXUp","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"A pop-up will appear in the center of your screen, prompting you to provide a group name."}},{"id":"JIyJS6Dv8i","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"Check the box labeled \"Private group\" if you wish to create a group that can not be joined without approval from you.","withBorder":false,"withBackground":true,"stretched":false}},{"id":"FkDNbF_S_Q","type":"Header","data":{"text":"Inviting Friends","level":2}},{"id":"ikeqAaXFc2","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Once your group has been created, you can invite friends by locating and clicking the \"Copy Invite Link\" button at the top left of your group screen. Its icon is a paper plane."}},{"id":"-HYmZSlgxb","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"Shortly after clicking, you should see a notification in the top right of your screen saying \"Copied; Text copied to clipboard\".","withBorder":false,"withBackground":true,"stretched":false}},{"id":"NOyi0pjKmA","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Now that the invite link is copied to your clipboard, you can open a direct message with a friend you want to invite, and paste the invite link for them to use."}},{"id":"wTOnKf7Oig","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"The invite link will appear as \"inv:\" followed by a long string of characters, but once sent it will show up as an interactive button labeled \"Join Group\".","withBorder":false,"withBackground":true,"stretched":false}},{"id":"6qrXiIaEEq","type":"Header","data":{"text":"Joining Groups","level":2}},{"id":"6p42-Tpdw-","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"If you were sent an invite link directly over Parallel's direct messaging system, you simply have to click on the \"Join Group\" button that was sent."}},{"id":"DHEGY84FBS","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"Upon clicking, you will be prompted once more to select \"Join\" in order to join the group.","withBorder":false,"withBackground":true,"stretched":false}},{"id":"HXuarGXnRB","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"If you were sent an invite link to a Parallel group outside of Parallel's direct messaging system, you can still join! You can copy the invite link, and locate the \"Join Group\" drop down option under the \"Add a Group\" icon."}},{"id":"f5zKjgzoV0","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"Upon selecting the \"Join Group\" drop down, you will be prompted to paste the group invitation code before clicking \"Join\".","withBorder":false,"withBackground":true,"stretched":false}}],"version":"2.22.2","title":"Creating and Joining Groups"}; runStart();